Author: Decker#3767
Content: if you want to delete this watch-only address from your wallet (i looked - it's `BOTS_BONDADDRESS` from BarterDEX) - you don't need to move funds. Just use `dumpwallet` to dump all privkeys and addresses. Delete watch only from the export file. After - delete your wallet.dat, restart daemon, and use `importwallet` to import all of your privkeys in the wallet.

Content: All of these can took only 3-5 mins ...
